As a car rental company, I want to have a software system that allows customers to:

a) View available cars by location, date, and type.
b) Choose pickup and drop-off locations.
c) Reserve a car online
d) Choose pickup and drop-off locations
e) Provide payment information
f) Receive confirmation of reservation
g) Provide feedback and rate their experience
h) View past rental history
i) Receive notifications and promotions


So that we can improve the customer experience, streamline our operations, and increase sales and customer loyalty. We are working for our client, if they are happy
we are motivated to do more and better. Any user request will be provided as a special one so we can serve in real time.
